  "notes": [
    "Composition archetype is the FIRST creative decision — everything else follows",
    "Never mix archetypes within single asset (dilutes impact)",
    "Platform format should constrain archetype choice (vertical = no editorial split)",
    "Learning Engine should track which archetypes convert best per industry",
    "New archetypes emerge slowly (1-2 per year) — validate via pattern analysis"
  ]
}
